<span id="freeTextContainer12226847831479142161">Engaging play about honor, duty, love and how they intersect. Rodrigo (Cid) and Ximena&apos;s relationship and inner conflict is the centerpiece of the play here and is by the far the most interesting part of the play. This play is a tragicomedy which means it ends on a rather happy note - I think this play would have been more powerful as a tragedy.</span>
